descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...black background with two grids of the same color and another two grid of a different color
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input grid size.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the input grid, identify the colors of the colored grids. we will call it color A and color B. Around the grids with color A, create a 3x3 square with color B, surrounding the color A grids. Around the grids with color B, create a 3x3 square with color A, surrounding the color B grids. Now we should have four 3x3 squares, in which two squares are A color with B colored grid in their centers.

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...two different color grid
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... same as input size
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...fill a grid with another color grid around a color grid.  connect the 3x3 square box by grey color and black color followed.
